commit.title: Remove omega and romega.
commit.message:
Remove omega and romega.

We move zify to micromega and rebind omega and romega to lia.

Lia cannot be boostrapped in exactly the same way as omega, so the
stdlib will have to be adapted so as not to rely on lia inside ZArith.
Laurent Théry offered to remove the admits there.
